{
  "texts": [
    "Still, flexibility and scalability are the matters that should be paid attention to.",
    "It is concerning therefore that while there have been high achievements in the achievement of machine learning as well as deep learning there is the need to come up with models as well as algorithms that are capable of being scaled to support numerous geometries.",
    "This is especially important in the context of the IoT and industrial networks, where limited resources are a typical occurrence.",
    "To guarantee the safety of these increasingly networked systems, intrusion detection technologies that function well in such situations are essential.",
    "Furthermore, there is a need to bridge the gap between theoretical improvements in intrusion detection systems and their implementation in real-world network security."
  ]
}